				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				ok this is straight from the gm's mouth. the bear, like many other spawns is randomized.but its done all based on percentages, based on the last spawn and rate of spawn. so i just hit a string of bad luck when i tried. it had died three times in a row on friday. so on saturday and sunday the chances of him spawnin was super slim. the chances get better with time. its all just luck. it is an 8hr spawn. give or take 15min.<BR>

